#1. By adding Link in the head section after title:

Ex: 

<head>
	<title>dikvks</title>
     
     <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="style.css">

 </head>
 
 
 
 #2. Using style into a tag :
 
 Ex:
 
 <h1 style="background-color:green; color:red;>text</h1>
 
 
 
 #3. Using <style> tag into the head section :
 
 <style>
 
 li{ background-color:green; color:red;}
 </style>
 
 
/* All in all , we say say that " we can use css by the mentioned ways*/
